EHF's #COVID19 in #Texas survey: 59% are very likely or somewhat likely to get a #vaccine. Hispanic (63%) & White (59%) Texans are more likely to get vaccine than Black Texans (49%).

Texans need important messaging to show the vaccine is safe & effective.
